article_id:1263,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing the Next Summon Showcase, Fire Emblem: Kindred Ties (Part One)!,image_path:,message:<div>The next Summon Showcase, Fire Emblem: Kindred Ties (Part One), kicks off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1588226400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This summon showcase will feature limited-time adventurers, and appearance rates for the featured adventurers will be boosted for the duration!</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The roster for this summon showcase will not include the limited-time 5★ adventurers from the Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes summon showcase, which is live at the same time.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1588226400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1589263140"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the newly featured limited-time adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
