				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>Prince of the Halidom of Ylisse, and leader of a<br>militia called the Shepherds. While he himself<br>worries that he comes across as cold, he's<br>idolized as a good man without pretense, and one<br>who fights at the forefront for the sake of peace.</li>
